;Ce centre permettra aux jeunes et aux femmes de la commune de Tattaguine ainsi que de la région de :</strong></p>\n                <p><strong style=\"font-weight: 400; color: rgb(53, 55, 68); font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">bénéficier de programmes de formation en phase avec la demande sur le marché du travai...l</strong></p>\n                <p>\n                  <br>\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"h-column h-column-container d-flex h-col-lg-3 h-col-md-3 h-col-12 style-193-outer style-local-32-c12-outer\">\n        <div data-colibri-id=\"32-c12\" class=\"d-flex h-flex-basis h-column__inner h-px-lg-3 h-px-md-3 h-px-2 v-inner-lg-3 v-inner-md-3 v-inner-2 style-193 style-local-32-c12 position-relative\">\n          <!---->\n          <!---->\n          <div class=\"w-100 h-y-container h-column__content h-column__v-align flex-basis-100 align-self-lg-center align-self-md-center align-self-center\">\n            <!---->\n            <div data-colibri-id=\"32-c13\" class=\"h-icon style-194 style-local-32-c13 position-relative h-element\">\n              <!----><span class=\"h-svg-icon h-icon__icon style-194-icon style-local-32-c13-icon\"><!--Icon by Font Awesome (https://fontawesome.com)--><svg version=\"1.1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" id=\"line-chart\" viewBox=\"0 0 2048 1896.0833\"><path d=\"M2048 1536v128H0V128h128v1408h1920zM1920 288v435q0 21-19.5 29.5T1865 745l-121-121-633 633q-10 10-23 10t-23-10l-233-233-416 416-192-192 585-585q10-10 23-10t23 10l233 233 464-464-121-121q-16-16-7.5-35.5T1453 256h435q14 0 23 9t9 23z\"></path></svg></span></div>\n            <div\n              data-colibri-id=\"32-c14\" class=\"h-global-transition-all h-heading style-195 style-local-32-c14 position-relative h-element\">\n              <!---->\n              <div class=\"h-heading__outer style-